data.description: Well kept three bed three bath home with quality updates throughout! This amazing home features: PLUSH comfortable carpet, durable faux tile laminate floors, spacious eat-in kitchen w/SOLID surface countertops, formal dining room, classy hall bath, spacious primary bedroom retreat with quality 3/4 bath, and roomy secondary bedrooms. The lower level boasts: OPEN family room, private office space, convenient 1/2 bath, handy laundry room, under stairs storage, and large windows for ample natural light. Exterior amenities include: multiple low maintenance vinyl double hung windows, large storage shed, LUSH green lawn w/sprinkler system, oversized deck (overlooking the fully fenced in backyard), and relaxing front deck/stoop peering at the tree lined Maple Village Park. With close and easy access to schools, parks, I-80 corridor, and ALL appliances included…this home is SURE to impress! AMA
